# Development Guide

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies with `npm install`
2. Start development server with `npm run dev`
3. Access the app at http://localhost:5173/

## Build Configuration

- Vite configuration: [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts)
- TypeScript configuration: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- ESLint configuration: [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js)
- Tailwind configuration: [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js)

## Adding Features

When adding new features:
1. Update type definitions in [types.ts](mdc:src/types.ts) if needed
2. Update database schema in [db.ts](mdc:src/db.ts) if needed
3. Add new UI components in [src/components/](mdc:src/components)
4. Update main application logic in [App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx)

## Building for Production

Run `npm run build` to create a production build in the `dist` directory.
